  "texts": [
    "This line of research is critical for developing effective error correction frameworks for LLMs like Kimi, which must handle the complex nuances of the Chinese language effectively and accurately.",
    "This section outlines the methodology for incorporating automated error correction and feedback loops into Kimi.",
    "The approach combines theoretical underpinnings with practical implementations, leveraging advanced algorithms and architectures to enhance the model's performance and reliability.",
    "System ArchitectureThe architecture of the proposed error correction system for Kimi is designed to be robust and scalable, incorporating multiple layers of processing to ensure accuracy and efficiency.",
    "The core components of the system include an error detection module, an error correction module, and a logging and feedback module."
